usdBgpAgent.name: usdBgpAgent

revisions.description: Added support for the BGP4-MIB. Added support for BGP internal redistribute. Obsoleted rsBgpStorageInitialHistoryRoutePoolSize and rsBgpStorageMaxHistoryRoutePoolSize. Added the ability to unconfigure BGP attributes from the MIB.
Added support for adding unicast BGP routes into a multicast view.
Added support for peer and peer-group local-as.
Replaced the BGP route congiguration group with new tables containing the original route destination as an additional index.
The initial release of this management information module.

usdBgpAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the BGP component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdBgpAgentV1.name: usdBgpAgentV1
usdBgpAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the BGP component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the BGP component was supported in the Unisphere
        RX 3.0 and 3.1 system releases.
usdBgpAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the BGP application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when a new object was added to the general configuration group.
